<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink322">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>neṭuṅkaḻai muḷiya vēṉi ṉīṭik</l>
<l>kaṭuṅkatir ñāyiṟu kalpakat teṟutaliṉ</l>
<l>veyya vāyiṉa muṉṉē yiṉiyē</l>
<l>yoṇṇuta larivaiyai yuḷḷutoṟun</l>
<l>taṇṇiya vāyiṉa curattiṭai yāṟē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>Before,</l>
    <l>the paths through the wasteland were hot,</l>
      <l>as summer lasted so long, the tall bamboos dried out,</l> 
        <l>and the sun with harsh rays scorched the stones [until they] split.</l> 
          <l>And now, every time I think about the girl with bright forehead,</l>
            <l>they become cool.</l>  
     
  </lg>
      </div>
